PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-2197 which substitutes the date "February 1, 1994" for "March 1, 1994" as the effective date of the appointment of MICHAEL STEPHEN SCHELEW as a full-time member and Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board.
